#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:2
#: 602eaa820bc645d68b31857b2815014a
msgid "播放控制"
msgstr "Playback Control"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:4
#: 32463cae74b14ce386bffd144ea5e2df
msgid "本章讲“怎样把声音播出来，以及播出来以后怎样控制它”。"
msgstr "This chapter explains how to play sounds and how to control them after they start playing."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:6
#: f83bac3ac6f54cec903758a994bc8c3d
msgid ""
"刚开始使用时，优先用播放节点。只有当你需要更细的控制，例如一次性创建 :ref:`Sound<glossary-sound>`、拿到 :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>`、手动设置循环点或 3D 属性时，再使用代码播放。"
msgstr ""
"When you are getting started, prefer playback nodes. Use code-driven playback only when you need finer control, such as creating a :ref:`Sound<glossary-sound>` yourself, getting a :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>`, or manually setting loop points or 3D properties."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:9
#: fc0d2ad604674b2888f4a09407d8f542
msgid "先选哪种播放方式"
msgstr "Choose a Playback Method First"

