"    var tween := create_tween()\n"
"    tween.tween_property(music, \"volume_db\", target_db, duration)"
msgstr ""
"func fade_music(target_db: float, duration: float):\n"
"    var tween := create_tween()\n"
"    tween.tween_property(music, \"volume_db\", target_db, duration)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:88
#: 9fad8661b8b74b1ab7258d8a0bd8f636
msgid "播放一次短音效"
msgstr "Play a Short Sound Effect Once"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:90
#: b5304353901c46d8a0ca993eb83e3de5
msgid "如果只是“按按钮、开枪、拾取物品”这种一次性短音效，可以放一个播放器节点，然后反复调用 ``play()``："
msgstr ""
"For one-shot sound effects such as pressing a button, firing a weapon, or picking up an item, you can place a player node and call ``play()`` repeatedly:"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:92
#: 3d80bc4990fb4a469a672f3543a2e38c
msgid ""
"extends Node\n"
"\n"
"@onready var hit := $HitPlayer\n"
"\n"
"func _ready():\n"
"    var stream := FmodAudioStream.new()\n"
"    stream.file_path = \"res://sfx/hit.wav\"\n"
"    hit.stream = stream\n"
"    hit.bus = \"SFX\"\n"
"\n"
"func play_hit():\n"
"    hit.play()"
msgstr ""
"extends Node\n"
"\n"
"@onready var hit := $HitPlayer\n"
"\n"
"func _ready():\n"
"    var stream := FmodAudioStream.new()\n"
"    stream.file_path = \"res://sfx/hit.wav\"\n"
"    hit.stream = stream\n"
"    hit.bus = \"SFX\"\n"
"\n"
"func play_hit():\n"
"    hit.play()"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:107
#: 7cc5dcf3447043e7922fa7b10a49372f
msgid "如果同一个声音可能重叠播放很多次，例如一秒内触发多发子弹，建议考虑代码播放或对象池，避免一个节点来不及处理所有重叠声音。"
msgstr ""
"If the same sound may overlap many times, such as several bullets fired in one second, consider code-driven playback or an object pool so one node does not have to handle every overlapping instance."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:110
#: c9cfb61de3d54f90b077e4e26f302e0c
msgid "用代码播放"
msgstr "Play from Code"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:112
#: ce41a19541934e5c835c532591f4abcf
msgid "代码播放会更接近 FMOD 的工作方式："
msgstr "Code-driven playback is closer to how FMOD works:"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:114
#: f0e3885294474e268e63468a65327875
msgid "用 :ref:`System<glossary-system>` 创建 :ref:`Sound<glossary-sound>`。"
msgstr "Create a :ref:`Sound<glossary-sound>` with the :ref:`System<glossary-system>`."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:115
#: e7c2ce963af842969d636accead821f4
msgid "选择输出到哪个 :ref:`Bus<glossary-bus>` / :ref:`ChannelGroup<glossary-channelgroup>`。"
msgstr "Choose which :ref:`Bus<glossary-bus>` / :ref:`ChannelGroup<glossary-channelgroup>` to output to."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:116
#: 289c8ee50c9f426fb9662c6d9bde93b0
msgid "调用 ``play_sound()``，得到这次播放的 :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>`。"
msgstr "Call ``play_sound()`` to get the :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>` for this playback instance."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:118
#: 8c00aa7fbc6e45e8b92137a1e79f4f5a
msgid ""
"func play_sound(path: String, bus_name: String = \"SFX\") -> FmodChannel:\n"
"    var system := FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"\n"
"    var sound := system.create_sound_from_file(path)\n"
"    var bus := system.get_channel_group_by_name(bus_name)\n"
"    var channel := system.play_sound(sound, bus, false)\n"
"\n"
"    return channel"
msgstr ""
"func play_sound(path: String, bus_name: String = \"SFX\") -> FmodChannel:\n"
"    var system := FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"\n"
"    var sound := system.create_sound_from_file(path)\n"
"    var bus := system.get_channel_group_by_name(bus_name)\n"
"    var channel := system.play_sound(sound, bus, false)\n"
"\n"
"    return channel"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:129
#: 0fcada036a134bdd85afd93e77096b97
msgid "返回的 ``channel`` 只代表“这一次播放”。同一个 ``sound`` 播放三次，就会有三个不同的 :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>`。"
msgstr ""
"The returned ``channel`` represents only this one playback instance. If the same ``sound`` is played three times, there will be three different :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>` objects."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:132
#: 55ec9c32191c4c90b1f0c51ce25d3ee1
msgid "先暂停再配置"
msgstr "Create Paused, Then Configure"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:134
#: f053fe778d13463089695310399c756b
msgid "有时你希望声音开始前先设置音量、音高或 3D 位置。可以让它以暂停状态创建，配置完成后再恢复："
msgstr ""
"Sometimes you need to set volume, pitch, or 3D position before the sound starts. Create it paused, configure it, and then resume playback:"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:136
#: cb5536fbb99d48bb92441d33a1dcea04
msgid ""
"func play_configured(path: String) -> FmodChannel:\n"
"    var system := FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"    var sound := system.create_sound_from_file(path)\n"
"    var sfx_bus := system.get_channel_group_by_name(\"SFX\")\n"
"\n"
"    var channel := system.play_sound(sound, sfx_bus, true)\n"
"    channel.volume_db = -6.0\n"
"    channel.pitch = 1.2\n"
"    channel.set_paused(false)\n"
"\n"
"    return channel"
msgstr ""
"func play_configured(path: String) -> FmodChannel:\n"
"    var system := FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"    var sound := system.create_sound_from_file(path)\n"
"    var sfx_bus := system.get_channel_group_by_name(\"SFX\")\n"
"\n"
"    var channel := system.play_sound(sound, sfx_bus, true)\n"
"    channel.volume_db = -6.0\n"
"    channel.pitch = 1.2\n"
"    channel.set_paused(false)\n"
"\n"
"    return channel"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:151
#: 726cc11380f94390bf8153793e3c4186
msgid "控制一次播放"
msgstr "Control One Playback Instance"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:153
#: 22ca7ce993794124a19a7f3ce5583390
msgid ":ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>` 是“一次正在播放的声音”。它可以暂停、停止、调音量、调音高、跳转位置，也可以设置 3D 属性。"
msgstr ""
"A :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>` is one currently playing sound. It can be paused, stopped, have its volume and pitch adjusted, seek to a position, and receive 3D properties."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:156
#: 7b9318a72dae4afba6c3cf7fb9bd1e51
msgid "暂停、恢复和停止"
msgstr "Pause, Resume, and Stop"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:158
#: 3c3a80521a3b4998a0019d357309b1a3
msgid ""
"func pause_channel(channel: FmodChannel, paused: bool):\n"
"    if channel != null:\n"
"        channel.set_paused(paused)\n"
"\n"
"func stop_channel(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    if channel != null:\n"
"        channel.stop()\n"
"\n"
"func is_still_playing(channel: FmodChannel) -> bool:\n"
"    return channel != null and channel.is_playing()"
msgstr ""
"func pause_channel(channel: FmodChannel, paused: bool):\n"
"    if channel != null:\n"
"        channel.set_paused(paused)\n"
"\n"
"func stop_channel(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    if channel != null:\n"
"        channel.stop()\n"
"\n"
"func is_still_playing(channel: FmodChannel) -> bool:\n"
"    return channel != null and channel.is_playing()"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:172
#: b31ea045e4094fc49c3c1bc8233c1990
msgid "音量、音高和声像"
msgstr "Volume, Pitch, and Pan"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:174
#: 9734f45407c441229a2b60ec11babb8f
msgid ""
"func adjust_channel(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    channel.volume_db = -10.0\n"
"    channel.pitch = 1.0\n"
"\n"
"    # -1.0 在左边，0.0 在中间，1.0 在右边。\n"
"    channel.set_pan(0.25)"
msgstr ""
"func adjust_channel(channel: FmodChannel): channel.volume_db = -10.0 channel.pitch = 1.0 # -1.0 in left , 0.0 in , 1.0 in right . channel.set_pan(0.25)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:183
#: 5cb19d7a655d4786bbce3801850ef0a2
msgid "``pitch`` 会同时影响音高和播放速度。``0.5`` 听起来更低也更慢，``2.0`` 听起来更高也更快。"
msgstr ""
"``pitch`` affects both pitch and playback speed. ``0.5`` sounds lower and slower, while ``2.0`` sounds higher and faster."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:186
#: bafd448f10fc484b815060708e9bbbea
msgid "播放位置"
msgstr "Playback Position"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:188
#: ea949233d8e743428b8d8a0c6762d295
msgid "位置通常用毫秒控制。适合音乐跳转、从某个时间点继续播放，或做简单的预览工具。"
msgstr ""
"Position is usually controlled in milliseconds. This is useful for music seeking, resuming from a specific time, or building a simple preview tool."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:190
#: 9bf653f87d614175bd55a574bb793a8a
msgid ""
"func jump_to_30_seconds(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    channel.set_position(30000, FmodChannel.TIMEUNIT_MS)\n"
"\n"
"func print_position(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    var position_ms := channel.get_position(FmodChannel.TIMEUNIT_MS)\n"
"    print(\"position: \", position_ms, \" ms\")"
msgstr ""
"func jump_to_30_seconds(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    channel.set_position(30000, FmodChannel.TIMEUNIT_MS)\n"
"\n"
"func print_position(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    var position_ms := channel.get_position(FmodChannel.TIMEUNIT_MS)\n"
"    print(\"position: \", position_ms, \" ms\")"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:200
#: f1aa1b198b1e424994d983918f32aaf2
msgid "循环"
msgstr "Looping"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:202
#: 3169e6953b8d418090115bbb3f32ea38
msgid ""
"func loop_forever(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    channel.loop_count = -1\n"
"\n"
"func loop_three_times(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    channel.loop_count = 3\n"
"\n"
"func disable_loop(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    channel.loop_count = 0"
msgstr ""
"func loop_forever(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    channel.loop_count = -1\n"
"\n"
"func loop_three_times(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    channel.loop_count = 3\n"
"\n"
"func disable_loop(channel: FmodChannel):\n"
"    channel.loop_count = 0"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:213
#: b67516a34ce44496b46a007891be7db2
msgid ""
"循环是否生效还和创建声音时使用的播放模式有关。常规节点播放通常更适合简单循环；需要精确控制循环点时，再直接控制 :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>` 和 :ref:`Sound<glossary-sound>`。"
msgstr ""
"Whether looping works also depends on the playback mode used when the sound was created. Regular node playback is usually better for simple loops; control :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>` and :ref:`Sound<glossary-sound>` directly only when you need precise loop points."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:216
#: 10cd55d7318046ea992156049fa5dd3a
msgid "2D 与 3D 播放"
msgstr "2D and 3D Playback"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:218
#: a5a2d92182bf4821a0295f95feb21bd3
msgid "2D 声音不跟随世界位置变化，适合 UI、音乐、旁白。3D 声音会根据 :ref:`Listener<glossary-listener>` 和声源的位置计算距离、方向和衰减。"
msgstr ""
"2D sounds do not follow world positions, so they are suitable for UI, music, and narration. 3D sounds calculate distance, direction, and attenuation from the :ref:`Listener<glossary-listener>` and the sound source position."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:221
#: 9691ec88fb3a4f3b8edde27bf8ffc53f
msgid "优先使用 3D 播放节点"
msgstr "Prefer the 3D Playback Node"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:223
#: ef86aa60a3a34be29392751599d14302
msgid "在 3D 场景里，最简单的方式是使用 :ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D>`。它会把节点位置同步给 FMOD。"
msgstr ""
"In a 3D scene, the simplest approach is to use :ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D>`. It synchronizes the node position to FMOD."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:225
#: 1219cb016ccb4b2b9bf0672c72a67246
msgid ""
"extends Node3D\n"
"\n"
"@onready var emitter := $FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D\n"
"\n"
"func play_at_current_position():\n"
"    emitter.bus = \"SFX\"\n"
"    emitter.play()"
msgstr ""
"extends Node3D\n"
"\n"
"@onready var emitter := $FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D\n"
"\n"
"func play_at_current_position():\n"
"    emitter.bus = \"SFX\"\n"
"    emitter.play()"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:235
#: a7f057aa112242f881b441a3cf8f96c7
msgid "如果声音应该跟随敌人、车辆、门、机关或环境物件，就把播放器作为这些节点的子节点。"
msgstr ""
"If a sound should follow an enemy, vehicle, door, mechanism, or environment object, make the player a child of that node."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:238
#: 2b04426a98f443a6b18b35b579850b39
msgid "代码方式设置 3D 位置"
msgstr "Set 3D Position from Code"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:240
#: 914fbd00416349f5927c017a9b37b143
msgid "只有在你直接代码播放时，才需要手动设置 3D 属性："
msgstr "You only need to set 3D properties manually when playing directly from code:"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:242
#: fd25db653d6f448d8d141d1323bb6b6a
msgid ""
"func play_3d_sound(path: String, position: Vector3):\n"
"    var system := FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"    var sound := system.create_sound_from_file(path, FmodSystem.MODE_3D)\n"
"    var bus := system.get_channel_group_by_name(\"SFX\")\n"
"\n"
"    var channel := system.play_sound(sound, bus, true)\n"
"    channel.set_3d_attributes(position, Vector3.ZERO)\n"
"    channel.set_3d_min_max_distance(1.0, 30.0)\n"
"    channel.set_paused(false)\n"
"\n"
"    return channel"
msgstr ""
"func play_3d_sound(path: String, position: Vector3):\n"
"    var system := FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"    var sound := system.create_sound_from_file(path, FmodSystem.MODE_3D)\n"
"    var bus := system.get_channel_group_by_name(\"SFX\")\n"
"\n"
"    var channel := system.play_sound(sound, bus, true)\n"
"    channel.set_3d_attributes(position, Vector3.ZERO)\n"
"    channel.set_3d_min_max_distance(1.0, 30.0)\n"
"    channel.set_paused(false)\n"
"\n"
"    return channel"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:256
#: faf71acb4cdc4a92bad2c7ecb493d515
msgid "这里的 ``MODE_3D`` 很重要。没有用 3D 模式创建的声音，即使设置了位置，也不会按 3D 声源来计算。"
msgstr ""
"``MODE_3D`` is important here. If a sound was not created in 3D mode, setting a position will not make it behave as a 3D sound source."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:259
#: 8e1dc8844f5d43fe85c08d54a5f325db
msgid "监听器"
msgstr "Listener"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:261
#: cadfb8ae5afc46089885c51acba97e11
msgid ":ref:`Listener<glossary-listener>` 表示玩家“从哪里听”。通常它跟随玩家角色或主摄像机。"
msgstr ""
"The :ref:`Listener<glossary-listener>` represents where the player hears from. It usually follows the player character or the main camera."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:263
#: 0a10a103a95a46d4b6d40123d11e4582
msgid ""
"extends CharacterBody3D\n"
"\n"
"func _physics_process(_delta):\n"
"    var system := FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"    system.set_3d_listener_attributes(\n"
"        0,\n"
"        global_position,\n"
"        velocity,\n"
"        -global_transform.basis.z,\n"
"        global_transform.basis.y\n"
"    )"
msgstr ""
"extends CharacterBody3D\n"
"\n"
"func _physics_process(_delta):\n"
"    var system := FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"    system.set_3d_listener_attributes(\n"
"        0,\n"
"        global_position,\n"
"        velocity,\n"
"        -global_transform.basis.z,\n"
"        global_transform.basis.y\n"
"    )"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:277
#: a67532e93a204efb9d11b39dee189dc2
msgid "如果 3D 声音听起来方向不对、距离不对，先检查监听器位置和朝向。"
msgstr "If a 3D sound has the wrong direction or distance, check the listener position and orientation first."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:280
#: a5cbcaff429e4915978890deec1d6d85
msgid "常见问题"
msgstr "FAQ"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:283
#: 2ee6f188d8444297b3f24190404ffa37
msgid "声音没有播放"
msgstr "The Sound Does Not Play"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:285
#: 6e1d38d6660044a19044e1827efe9bd7
msgid "按顺序检查："
msgstr "Check these in order:"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:287
#: ac741a25118044c582901e71f276e282
msgid "音频路径是否正确。"
msgstr "Whether the audio path is correct."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:288
#: 1e9fd24e44704cd699d9fff26c649886
msgid "播放节点是否有 ``stream``。"
msgstr "Whether the playback node has a ``stream``."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:289
#: 1406ce9d9a99413b9b2fd8867172ebbb
msgid "目标 :ref:`Bus<glossary-bus>` 是否存在，是否被静音。"
msgstr "Whether the target :ref:`Bus<glossary-bus>` exists and is not muted."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:290
#: 633aceba56794042a6b8eb5aed0ca661
msgid "音量是否太低。"
msgstr "Whether the volume is too low."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:291
#: 86123610efbe4a699ebbc68679d8d2c4
msgid "3D 声音是否离 :ref:`Listener<glossary-listener>` 太远。"
msgstr "Whether the 3D sound is too far away from the :ref:`Listener<glossary-listener>`."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:294
#: 67172531a639408aa3992a7dfde19f58
msgid "声音只能播放一次"
msgstr "The Sound Only Plays Once"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:296
#: 35a0dfa0134c484a8b1b77972ca65930
msgid ""
"如果同一个节点还在播放，再调用 ``play()`` 可能会重启这一次播放，而不是创建新的重叠声音。需要重叠播放时，可以创建多个播放器、使用对象池，或直接用 ``play_sound()`` 获取多个 :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>`。"
msgstr ""
"If the same node is still playing, calling ``play()`` again may restart that playback instead of creating a new overlapping sound. For overlapping playback, create multiple players, use an object pool, or call ``play_sound()`` directly to obtain multiple :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>` objects."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:299
#: 13a0ef9844664ddda6e3dd8767bd90a6
msgid "大量声音时卡顿"
msgstr "Stutter When Playing Many Sounds"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:301
#: f3a73eaed94c4789a7ba23fc4fef8113
msgid "短音效可以优先用 Sample 方式或预加载；长音乐优先用 Stream 方式。两者的区别见 :ref:`Stream 与 Sample<glossary-stream-sample>`。"
msgstr ""
"For short sound effects, prefer Sample mode or preloading. For long music, prefer Stream mode. See :ref:`Stream and Sample<glossary-stream-sample>` for the difference."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:303
#: 57724b400158490b92ddd8e9b7456137
msgid "同时播放很多声音时，也可以关注 :ref:`Virtual Channel<glossary-virtual-channel>`。FMOD 可能会让听不见或优先级低的声音进入虚拟状态，以减少混音开销。"
msgstr ""
"When many sounds play at once, also pay attention to :ref:`Virtual Channel<glossary-virtual-channel>`. FMOD may virtualize inaudible or low-priority sounds to reduce mixing cost."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:306
#: fb78194477c14f6d8ffca51d7217698c
msgid "建议"
msgstr "Recommendations"

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:308
#: d9b98ae44d324132babf1f0a835f5663
msgid "入门先用播放节点，不要一开始就直接操作底层对象。"
msgstr "Start with playback nodes. Do not operate on lower-level objects right away."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:309
#: 30d5a3e4666e42f09863d3d3ca238a53
msgid "需要控制“这一次播放”时，再拿 :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>`。"
msgstr "Get a :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>` when you need to control this specific playback instance."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:310
#: 5685e04ecccb44a1a234e8cfde7bd6be
msgid "长音乐走 ``Music`` 总线，短音效走 ``SFX`` 总线。"
msgstr "Route long music to the ``Music`` bus and short sound effects to the ``SFX`` bus."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:311
#: 298575bf8de14ec4afdc0dc3beccc693
msgid "3D 声音优先用 :ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D>`。"
msgstr "Prefer :ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D>` for 3D sounds."

#: ../../source/user_guide/playback.rst:312
#: a1fa7c6c702f4e0a972caa41335dc972
msgid "代码播放时，如果要先配置参数，就用暂停状态创建，再恢复播放。"
msgstr "When playing from code, create the sound paused if you need to configure parameters first, then resume playback."
